{"tid":2198460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"指中國是日本安全威脅！日防相：違反規則須付出代價","createTime":"2020-09-11T11:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T11:39:46.000Z","uid":261647,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0c96ce28b86ecba69876b6467fd03f5e32994e60","tid":2198460,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3287167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287167&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=5fc6b984\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287167&h=08204db3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3287167</a><br />\n<br />\n日本防衛大臣河野太郎9日對中國發表鷹派的強硬言論，他指中國對日本的安全構成威脅，北京企圖將海上軍事活動擴大到東海，有必要強化印度太平洋地區的區域合作。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，河野太郎9日在美國戰略與國際研究中心（CSIS）的線上研討會表示，當他擔任外務大臣的時候，他只說「嚴重關切」中國，沒有將中國稱作「威脅」，但他作為防衛大臣，必須說中國已成為日本的一個安全威脅。<br />\n<br />\n他強調有共同理念的國家應推動聯合能力，特別是在印度太平洋地區。河野太郎說，為了制止中國的擴張，當中國違反國際規則和準則時，必須讓北京付出一些代價，但僅靠日本和美國做不到，必須團結國際社會，建立更大的區域機制或全球機制。他提倡美國、日本、澳洲、印度的「四方聯盟」（Quad）應該有更密切的合作關係。<br />\n<br />\n關於中國試圖以武力和脅迫改變現狀的行動，河野太郎指出，從今年4月到6月的90天內，日本自衛隊共出動戰機177次應對中國戰機，近年來日本戰機每年都出動700次左右，比冷戰時期還要多。河野太郎還說，中國近幾十年來在國防方面的支出大幅增加，中國國防支出為日本的4倍，雙方差距很大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://youtu.be/izqXpgUjQPo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FizqXpgUjQPo&h=5a5c462f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/09/10/phpN6VaCh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F09%2F10%2FphpN6VaCh.png&h=65639cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本防衛大臣河野太郎9日對中國發表鷹派的強硬言論。（圖擷取自CSIS）"},{"pid":"9f6ced7b77a0eaecdc513c2648252330902396a8","tid":2198460,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfe623457a65884c822a1dc23e2324122bc0afc","tid":2198460,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e211bcfe981c1a19a22a2745d40acaddb032ef","tid":2198460,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:16:57.000Z","msg":"然後繼續任支那資本滲透<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c7a1e00c71e5d8e89bfcf491245be6cc658c79","tid":2198460,"uid":40267,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:18:36.000Z","msg":"收翻北海道支那人啲地先啦"},{"pid":"7492e65b8ba591ea12db1cb99639fd1c2908ac96","tid":2198460,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:26:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"815f6ee49dd904b65de84ae533125e6a10bab451","tid":2198460,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be89535995605904bbb8dd94cf43b813f8102ba","tid":2198460,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"東京大阪嘅支那人仲多過local呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a600a86c3302441a41604a97deb1750fb02e2a","tid":2198460,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:27:26.000Z","msg":"當主持人問及日本是否會為了沖繩縣的尖閣與中國開戰時，河野說：&quot;日本準備保衛哪怕是一厘米的土地，日美兩國政府基於同盟關係，為了尖閣會毫不猶豫地使用武力。 如果我們什麼都不做，它可能成為的另一個南海。"},{"pid":"1923b36bc0978